body:
🌿tag yourself: conan gray’ songs 🌿

✨ the other side: warm heart, apple juice, overthink, old libraries, summer breezes, oversized hoodie, pastel colors, cartoons, cozy and soft aesthetic, journal.

✨lovesick boys: love letters, soft smiles, lots of sunlight, enamel mugs, warm hot chocolate, cute glasses, curly hair, blooming flowers, long baths with rose petals, birdsong.

✨ you think i’m crazy: a bit sad inside, lonely, rainy days, lying on the roof the house and look at the moon, soft inside, deep feelings, old soul, autumn, midnight drives, fog.

✨ idle town: slow dancing, ice-cream, dreaming, telling yourself everything will be okay, loves learning new thing, sarcastic but kind, best hug, sunrise, yellow converse, summer.

✨ grow: nostalgia, collects vinyls, road trips, run away to dawn, indeterminacy, messy hair, load laughter, meeting with friends in a café, big dreams, dancing alone in your room.

✨ i know a place: sleepy eyes, acoustic playlist, iced coffee, getting lost in a good book, calm and silence, kind heart, green grass, sound of the oceans, sad smiles, freedom.
